{"tid":1013541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子伏屍柏景灣巴士總站電錶房頂　疑剪偷電線觸電亡","createTime":"2019-02-08T11:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T12:10:59.000Z","uid":81228,"like":185,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"dbb6891af2d724562ef8549c12719526fd95b1bd","tid":1013541,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/photo/bkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190208190954\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190208190954&h=54a648a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴士總站電錶房頂驚現男屍，不排除事主剪偷電線觸電亡。(曾紹良/馬竟峯攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/photo/bkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190208190954\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190208190954&h=0cb8e181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者遺體由帳篷遮蓋。（曾紹良攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/photo/bkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_03b.jpg?20190208190954\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20190208190954&h=8d9d84a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方將檢獲鉗吊下。(馬竟峯攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/photo/bkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_04b.jpg?20190208190954\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20190208190954&h=bc85b3d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n檢獲的兩把鉗。(馬竟峯攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/photo/bkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_05b.jpg?20190208190954\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20190208190954&h=3da0d6f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方及消防在現場調查。（曾紹良攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/photo/bkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_06b.jpg?20190208190954\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20190208190954&h=65be7fde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防員爬上電錶房頂調查。（曾紹良攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/photo/bkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_07b.jpg?20190208190954\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_07b.jpg%3F20190208190954&h=e49b1af9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防在現場調查。（讀者宋先生提供）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/photo/bkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_08b.jpg?20190208190954\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_08b.jpg%3F20190208190954&h=078e1130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方登電錶房頂調查。(馬竟峯攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/photo/bkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_09b.jpg?20190208190954\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001_09b.jpg%3F20190208190954&h=86ab7417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n探員將檢獲的兩鉗帶走調查。(馬竟峯攝)<br />\n<br />\n旺角海庭道18號柏景灣巴士總站，今早(8日)9時45分，有巴士公司職員嗅到異味，懷疑是電錶房發生事故，於是通知機電署等相關部門人員到場，追查異味來源，當人員沿鐵梯爬上電錶房頂部視察時，驚見一名男子倒臥上址，立即報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n消防及救護員到場，證實男子已死去多日，死者遺體其後由消防移至地面，並用帳篷遮蓋。警方在現場調查，旺角警區刑事調查隊探員於下午5時許爬上電錶房頂，檢獲兩把大剪鉗，放入證物袋內帶走，正調查有關物件是否屬於死者。據了解，警方在死者身上無發現身份證明文件，懷疑有人到上址圖偷電線，意外觸電身亡。<br />\n<br />\n據東網讀者宋先生表示，由於家住富榮花園，故每日也會到該巴士總站乘車，近兩周已開始嗅到陣陣異味，直至今早有街坊忍無可忍，追查異味來源始揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/bkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190208%2Fbkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1MemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=5d6cb1a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/bkn-20190208101416174-0208_00822_001.html?refer=hn2</a>"},{"pid":"5217e1481d4448508a27b8c87fddfaaa6dbc5e02","tid":1013541,"uid":40470,"like":184,"dislike":0,"score":184,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n抵撚死"},{"pid":"fb3ae4853e6cb59ab1ed363ac79303a256af452c","tid":1013541,"uid":7814,"like":225,"dislike":11,"score":214,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:01:56.000Z","msg":"偷電，抵撚死<br />\n希望死果陣係慢慢烤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d813b38b14766f37c10d7a16c10ebfc7af14a9","tid":1013541,"uid":213597,"like":8,"dislike":28,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5273fbe9a2c58980b81e710e939924545dff1afa","tid":1013541,"uid":12021,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76e452a62b9ce77da19b43de015146327007c0c5","tid":1013541,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"biohazard..."},{"pid":"a8694203986a51721fa17a66b6bafb65743682d9","tid":1013541,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:05:40.000Z","msg":"嗰頭唔係全部都住宅私樓咩<br />\n偷電做咩？<br />\n有露宿者？"},{"pid":"603576969e3ffb30d1309cdf35f6cca2a8d39130","tid":1013541,"uid":35774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a9f531f9fb4de395ca0e12d78f1aee73ebf302","tid":1013541,"uid":12786,"l